libftdi
------------------------------------------
libFTDI is an open source library to talk to FTDI chips: FT232BM, FT245BM,
FT2232C, FT2232D, FT245R and FT232H including the popular bitbang mode. The
library is linked with your program in userspace, no kernel driver required.

Runtime requirements:
  bash-4.3.42-3
  cygwin-2.2.1-1
  libconfuse0-2.7+git20140604-1bl1
  libftdi1-devel-1.2-1bl1
  libftdi1_2-1.2-1bl1
  libgcc1-4.9.3-1
  libstdc++6-4.9.3-1
  libusb1.0-1.0.19-1
  libusb1.0-devel-1.0.19-1
  python-2.7.10-1
  python-libftdi-1.2-1bl1
  python3-3.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.25-2
  cmake-3.3.1-1
  cygport-0.20.2-1
  gcc-core-4.9.3-1
  gcc-g++-4.9.3-1
  make-4.1-1

Canonical website:
  http://www.intra2net.com/en/developer/libftdi/

Canonical download:
  http://www.intra2net.com/en/developer/libftdi/download/libftdi1-1.2.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libftdi-1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libftdi-1.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libftdi-1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libftdi-1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libftdi1_2-1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libftdi1-devel-1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/python-libftdi-1.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libftdi)
  /usr/bin/ftdi_eeprom.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libftdi.README
  /usr/share/doc/libftdi/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libftdi/COPYING.LIB
  /usr/share/doc/libftdi/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libftdi/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libftdi/README
  /usr/share/doc/libftdi/TODO
  /usr/share/libftdi/examples/complete.py
  /usr/share/libftdi/examples/simple.py

(libftdi1_2)
  /usr/bin/cygftdi1-2.dll
  /usr/bin/cygftdipp1-2.dll

(libftdi1-devel)
  /usr/bin/libftdi1-config
  /usr/include/libftdi1/ftdi.h
  /usr/include/libftdi1/ftdi.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/libftdi1/LibFTDI1Config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/libftdi1/LibFTDI1ConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/libftdi1/UseLibFTDI1.cmake
  /usr/lib/libftdi1.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libftdipp1.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libftdi1.pc
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libftdipp1.pc

(python-libftdi)
  /usr/lib/python3.4/site-packages/_ftdi1.dll
  /usr/lib/python3.4/site-packages/ftdi1.py

